node_9.description: This is Sam Moore's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 5:00 am, go for a walk around Johnson Park at 6:00 am, have breakfast at 7:00 am, tend to the park at 8:00 am, spend time catching up with neighbors and telling them about his plans to run for local mayor at 10:00 am, have lunch at 12:00 pm, continue chatting with neighbors and reading at Hobbs cafe at 1:00 pm, return home for dinner with his wife at 5:00 pm.
